{"arkId":"cl010112452","url":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/ark:\/53355\/cl010112452","modified ":"2025-08-25","title":"Montre polylob\u00e9e","titleComplement":"","denominationTitle":[{"type":"Titre","value":"Montre polylob\u00e9e"}],"displayDateCreated":"Epoque \/ p\u00e9riode : Henri IV (1589-1610) (Occident-\u003ERenaissance-\u003Edynastie des Bourbons) ; Louis XIII (1610-1643) (Occident-\u003E\u00e9poque moderne = Ancien R\u00e9gime-\u003Edynastie des Bourbons)\r\n\r\nDate de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication : 1600 - 1625","currentLocation":"Richelieu, [OArt] Salle 531 - Paul Garnier, Vitrine 4","room":"Salle 531, Aile Aile Richelieu, Niveau 1","isMuseesNationauxRecuperation":false,"dateCreated":[{"startYear":1600,"endYear":1625,"imprecision":"","text":"1er quart du XVIIe si\u00e8cle","type":"Date de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication","doubt":""}],"creator":[{"label":"Faucon","attributionLevel":"Attribution actuelle","linkType":"","creatorRole":"Horloger","authenticationType":"","doubt":"","attributedBy":"","attributedYear":"","wikidata":""}],"objectNumber":[{"value":"OA 7048","type":"Num\u00e9ro principal"}],"collection":"D\u00e9partement des Objets d\u0027art du Moyen Age, de la Renaissance et des temps modernes","printsDrawingsEntity":"","printsDrawingsCollection":"","objectType":"horlogerie ; montre","originalObject":"","printState":"","description":"Montre polylob\u00e9e ; deux couvercles ovales grav\u00e9s compos\u00e9s de six lobes soulign\u00e9s de bordures convergeant vers une fleur \u00e0 six p\u00e9tales. Carrure orn\u00e9e d\u0027une frise grav\u00e9e de rinceaux peupl\u00e9s. Lobes d\u00e9cor\u00e9s de figures animales et humaines parmi des rinceaux fleuris. Pendant ajour\u00e9 ; bouton moulur\u00e9. Revers des couvercles portant un d\u00e9cor de volutes feuillag\u00e9s, poin\u00e7onn\u00e9es. Plaque du cadran grav\u00e9e d\u0027un Amour, d\u0027un enfant tenant une corne et de rinceaux fleuris ; portant un disque horaire \u00e0 chiffres romains entourant un paysage. Ajust\u00e9 dans le bo\u00eetier, mouvement \u00e0 \u00e9chappement \u00e0 verge, fus\u00e9e avec corde \u00e0 boyau. Coq ajour\u00e9 et grav\u00e9 de rinceaux, cliquet sans d\u00e9cor.","inscriptions":"Signature : \r ; mouvement sign\u00e9 : faucon\/A rennes [signature ponctu\u00e9e d\u0027une fleurette]","namesAndTitles":"","onomastics":"","dimension":[{"type":"Hauteur","value":"6","displayDimension":"6 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":1,"note":""},{"type":"Largeur","value":"3,2","displayDimension":"3,2 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":2,"note":""},{"type":"Epaisseur","value":"2,1","displayDimension":"2,1 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":3,"note":""}],"shape":"","materialsAndTechniques":"Mat\u00e9riau : argent\r\nMat\u00e9riau : laiton","placeOfCreation":"Rennes (Bretagne-\u003EIlle-et-Vilaine = Ille et Vilaine)","dateOfDiscovery":"","placeOfDiscovery":"","provenance":"","historicalContext":[],"objectHistory":"Collection Emile Gavet (1830-1904) ; collection Paul Garnier (1834-1916), \u00e0 Paris. Don Paul Garnier, en 1916.","jabachInventory":"","napoleonInventory":"","previousOwner":[{"value":"M. Garnier, Paul ","note":"","role":", Donateur"},{"value":"M. Gavet, Emile","note":"","role":", Collectionneur"}],"acquisitionDetails":[{"mode":"don","doubt":"","dates":[{"type":"date","value":"1916","startYear":1916,"endYear":1916}]}],"ownedBy":"Etat","heldBy":"Mus\u00e9e du Louvre, D\u00e9partement des Objets d\u0027art du Moyen Age, de la Renaissance et des temps modernes","longTermLoanTo":"","index":{"Mode d\u0027acquisition":[{"value":"don"}],"period":[{"value":"Henri IV (1589-1610)"},{"value":"Louis XIII (1610-1643)"}],"place":[{"value":"Rennes"}],"objectType":[{"value":"horlogerie"},{"value":"montre"}]},"bibliography":[{"bibliographyRef":"Cardinal, Catherine, Les montres et horloges de table du mus\u00e9e du Louvre, Tome 2, Paris, RMN, 2000","bibliogr